OL,5,G1830 Home and Away
OL,6,     FHarper avoids a hard truth. Alf
OL,7,     Fand Roo work to heal. Tane
OL,8,     Fsupports Mackenzie.
OL,9,G1900 GPs Behind Closed Doors
OL,10,     FThis week, the spotlight falls on
OL,11,     Fthe unsung heroes of general
OL,12,     Fpractice - the surgery
OL,13,     Freceptionists. Bernie deals with
OL,14,     Fan angry woman whose appointment
OL,15,     Fseems to have disappeared from the
OL,16,     Fsystem.
