OL,5,G2000 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,6,     FDr Nick Mani receives a critically
OL,7,     Fill one-day-old baby, and cricket
OL,8,     Flegend Dickie Bird is in for a
OL,9,     Ffollow-up. Documentary series
OL,10,     Ffilmed inside Barnsley casualty
OL,11,     Fdepartment.
OL,12,G2100 A&E After Dark
OL,13,     FPolice are called to Belfast's
OL,14,     FRoyal Victoria Emergency
OL,15,     FDepartment when a female patient
OL,16,     Fbecomes very aggressive, but Dr
OL,17,     FRachel recognises she's suffering
OL,18,     Ffrom a mental health crisis.
